      "date": "2012-11-25 17:48:35.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 7: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/c09608de-371f-11e2-8203-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  2 tests failed: sanityn, sanity.",
