      "date": "2012-12-08 21:28:48.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 9: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/e4113932-4179-11e2-af91-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
