        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2012-12-18 21:06:27.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 9: (1 inline comment)\n\nOh, test_25b \"change ACL under remote dir on one mountpoint be seen on another\" is used for testing remote/local LOOKUP lock.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 9
    },
